body:
I am currently Gold 1 with a mid-low plat MMR and every game I go into, almost everyone has a diamond or plat border. Sounds cool right? Wow this guy was silver last season and is now facing players who were plat last season.

Wrong. 

Every game I go into... &quot;Wow we have a silver on our team?&quot; or &quot;GG why do I always get silvers on my team&quot;
I do well in most games, usually carrying or contributing greatly to my team. But god forbid if I do poorly in a SINGLE GAME...

&quot;Of course we lose this with a silver&quot; and &quot;GG 9x report silver feeding&quot;

Please just remove my border.
